3. Da bih naučio engleski jezik, odlučio sam da upišem *engleski* kurs. (To learn English language, I decided to enroll in an English course.)
4. Nisam siguran da li mi se više dopada *engleska* ili francuska kuhinja. (I'm not sure if I like English or French cuisine more.)
5. Ovaj telefon je proizveden u *Engleskoj*. (This phone was manufactured in England.)
6. Svetsko prvenstvo u fudbalu se održava u *Engleskoj* ove godine. (The World Cup in soccer is taking place in England this year.)
7. U našem hotelu se nude različiti doručci, uključujući i *engleski* doručak. (Our hotel offers a variety of breakfasts, including an English breakfast.)
8. *Engleskim* turistima se dopada da posete Beograd. (English tourists enjoy visiting Belgrade.)
9. Juče sam gledao film o *engleskom* kralju. (Yesterday, I watched a movie about an English king.)
10. *Engleskih* fudbalera ima mnogo u najboljim evropskim klubovima. (There are many English soccer players in the best European clubs.)